data.description: Immaculate almost brand new home just minutes from Randolph AFB. This charming house features all the spaces you need with three bedrooms, two baths, and a full size kitchen/living/breakfast room plus a two car garage. All appliances are included in addition to a full sprinkler system and water softener. This home is turn key! And the best part? The backyard! This yard is MASSIVE with no neighbors to your left or behind you. Make this yard the backyard oasis of your dreams. The interior includes fresh paint and durable luxury vinyl plank flooring in the main living areas making it a great option as a rental as well. Schedule a private tour of this home today!
